{"tid":236219,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原作者決定要將PEPE殺死","createTime":"2017-05-09T14:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T14:19:48.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb7ea6cfc7a5cd94253c91632017ad0858e61fbf","tid":236219,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:38:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">原作者「搶救」無效，為「青蛙Pepe」舉行喪禮<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/67905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F67905&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BVzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=a0c8b870\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/67905</a></div></span><br />\n<br />\n漫畫家Matt Furie在2005年創作的角色「青蛙Pepe」（Pepe the Frog）自誕生以來一直受到網絡歡迎，不少人畫出不同版本的Pepe。不過近年美國的「另類右派」（alt-right）興起，這批白人至上主義者擅於運用網絡語言和製作meme，更挪用Pepe作為其「代言人」。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media4.s-nbcnews.com/j/msnbc/components/video/201609/a_ov_pepe_160928.nbcnews-ux-1080-600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia4.s-nbcnews.com%2Fj%2Fmsnbc%2Fcomponents%2Fvideo%2F201609%2Fa_ov_pepe_160928.nbcnews-ux-1080-600.jpg&h=75b32a99&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n去年10月，Furie在《Time》撰文，表示希望從另類右派手上「重奪」Pepe這個符號，不希望牠成為仇恨的象徵。他總結︰「本來Pepe只是一個笑話和一個悲傷快樂的象徵，我明白它已超出了我的控制，最終你說Pepe是什麼它就是什麼，而我&mdash;&mdash;Pepe的創造者&mdash;&mdash;說它代表愛。」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media3.giphy.com/media/fYFwoatsat4qI/200_s.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia3.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FfYFwoatsat4qI%2F200_s.gif&h=fd4b8c75&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n為了「拯救」Pepe，除了畫下Pepe的「特朗普噩夢」外，Furie亦跟把Pepe列入「網絡仇恨符號資料庫」的反誹謗聯盟（Anti-Defamation League）合作，發起#SavePepe行動。<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<a href=\"https://thenib.com/pepe-the-frog-to-sleep-perchance-to-meme\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthenib.com%2Fpepe-the-frog-to-sleep-perchance-to-meme&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BVzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=8d894fe4\" target=\"_blank\">https://thenib.com/pepe-the-frog-to-sleep-perchance-to-meme</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/85P8A4F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F85P8A4F.png&h=e97f7e07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F0EUGut.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF0EUGut.png&h=d9405901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M127mL0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM127mL0.png&h=64bed56c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cBkixiS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcBkixiS.png&h=b9e054d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97Tw7AF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97Tw7AF.png&h=13f98f29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"8a71fb2863babbe3857a9f0dbec4d5af0789c901","tid":236219,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:38:42.000Z","msg":"不過這一切似乎徒勞無功，另類右派繼續利用Pepe作宣傳，例如法國總統大選期間，網上就出現了「Pepe Le Pen」&mdash;&mdash;Pepe版本的極右國民陣線候選人勒龐（Marine Le Pen）&mdash;&mdash;看來是呼應美國總統選舉期間的「特朗普Pepe」。<br />\n<br />\n兩日前，Furie在其Tumblr上貼出其最新漫畫，顯示Pepe躺在棺材中。雖然他沒有正式宣佈Pepe的死訊，但貼文附上漫畫新聞網CBR的相關報道，標題為「Pepe已死︰Furie殺死了被白人至上主義者騎劫的符號」。<br />\n<br />\n這篇漫畫刊於出版商Fantagraphics在「免費漫畫書日」（Free Comic Book Day）推出的《World's Greatest Cartoonists》。Furie其後亦貼出全篇漫畫，畫出Pepe的喪禮，附上標籤#savepepe︰<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://image1.thenewslens.com/2017/5/jsfjpm4cfxzhhnrbbb8tzhubqi2gm6.jpg?q=100&amp;w=1080\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage1.thenewslens.com%2F2017%2F5%2Fjsfjpm4cfxzhhnrbbb8tzhubqi2gm6.jpg%3Fq%3D100%26w%3D1080&h=b4a9bd41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n不過無論Furie如何「殺死」Pepe，相信也無法阻止別人挪用牠來宣揚極端意識形態&mdash;&mdash;正如他的「拯救行動」一樣。在網絡上，Pepe這個卡通人物早已脫離原作者控制，有自己的生命。"},{"pid":"84a7bbe070fedc67323f3f555efca42495527ac4","tid":236219,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://media.breitbart.com/media/2016/10/sad-pepe-640x480.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.breitbart.com%2Fmedia%2F2016%2F10%2Fsad-pepe-640x480.jpg&h=f76ad1b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f69f3a8ce1097edadb97fb2c7e984d294f2dab81","tid":236219,"uid":331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:40:34.000Z","msg":"象仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1e5c7b7f49804db3ba10b180b49e2b6308c088","tid":236219,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:43:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/08/172433_f98567df24384ec7b42fd71f3fbf646c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F08%2F172433_f98567df24384ec7b42fd71f3fbf646c.jpg&h=c804ee94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6753t0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6753t0.jpg&h=0ba420bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a4072d98a9c805dfeee6d5ca3126ce6c6470871","tid":236219,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:46:11.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2016/10/24, 國際<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">「青蛙Pepe」創作者，<br />\n為何要從特朗普支持者手上「重奪」筆下人物？</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/52292\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F52292&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BVzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=30aaf1e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/52292</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image2.thenewslens.com/2016/10/0vg32bv10h04dcfa2wmadqn23yj7al.jpg?auto=compress&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=648&amp;q=100&amp;updated_at=2016-10-24-18-32-35&amp;w=1080\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.thenewslens.com%2F2016%2F10%2F0vg32bv10h04dcfa2wmadqn23yj7al.jpg%3Fauto%3Dcompress%26fit%3Dcrop%26h%3D648%26q%3D100%26updated_at%3D2016-10-24-18-32-35%26w%3D1080&h=e718b039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">這隻看起來無傷大雅的青蛙，由於變成了一小撮極右用作宣揚歧視、仇恨思想的符號，其創作者希望可以「重奪」筆下人物。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n相信大家對這隻青蛙並不陌生，由於表情太有「潛力」，許多年輕人都會把牠的圖片當成表情符號，在社交網站或即時通訊軟件上轉發。不過，牠近日被非政府組織「反誹謗聯盟」（Anti-Defamation League）列入網絡仇恨符號資料庫，原來他成為了「另類右派」（Alt-right）的代表，更被利用為美國總統候選人特朗普（Donald Trump）的助選工具。<br />\n<br />\n這隻青蛙名叫Pepe the Frog，是漫畫家Matt Furie在2005年的連載漫畫《男孩俱樂部》（Boy&rsquo;s Club）的主角之一，漫畫描述Pepe在小便時把褲脫到腳踝的位置，最後Pepe說的一句「Feels good, man」，連同其表情成為了「萬能Key」，在多個網站上爆紅。許多網友以牠為主角製作不同圖片，成為著名的表情包，Pepe甚至成為電子遊戲、紙牌遊戲的主角，也有自己的官方服裝和毛絨玩具。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i1.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/facebook/000/001/148/466px-Feels_good_man_full_comic.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Ffacebook%2F000%2F001%2F148%2F466px-Feels_good_man_full_comic.jpg&h=d5e44447&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n在特朗普宣布參選總統後的4個月，在其Twitter上載了一張「特朗普版Pepe」，並寫道︰「你不能阻止特朗普。」（You Can&rsquo;t Stump the Trump），其後「另類右派」把Pepe不斷改成支持特朗普的圖片，為這隻青蛙添上了濃厚的政治意味。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hg9OYhX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHg9OYhX.png&h=c10a0ef6&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"5f7bf588c924f3296f9d6589ab4c502a1f807c2c","tid":236219,"uid":43825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6c0ae9c17720ab5a182d2dbe6e836572958b4d","tid":236219,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:48:52.000Z","msg":"Reddit The Donald sub <img src=\"/assets/fac